<div class="container">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-12 "><h2 class="forget_me_not title">Three piles to interact with</h2><hr></div>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-sm-12 col-md-4">
             <%= image_tag('practicepile.png', class: 'img-circle img-responsive imright') %>
            <h3>Practice Pile</h3>
            <h4>Things I'm learning</h4>
            <p>Pile consisting of <strong>5</strong> cards at a time.</br> </p>
            <p>It is the pile you interact with the most. Just practice by viewing the cards in this stack and these views will be automatically tracked. After a card is viewed 15 times, it is moved to the "I know it" pile and another card from the "Reserve" pile is added. <p ><%= link_to("Practice now", practice_path(current_user.id), :class => "btn btn-xl btn-info", :id => "indigo") %></p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-12 col-md-4">
            <%= image_tag('reservepile.png', class: 'img-circle img-responsive flashcard imright') %>
            <h3>Reserve Pile</h3>
            <h4>Things I want to learn</h4>
            <p>These are the cards you want to learn. They will automatically be added to the Practice pile when needed. To build this pile, enter the facts you want to learn using the "Add card" button.</p>
            <p><%= link_to('Add cards', reserve_path(current_user.id), :class => "btn btn-large btn-info first", :id => "indigo"  ) %></p>
        </div>
        <div class="clearfix hidden-md hidden-lg"></div>
        <div class="col-sm-12 col-md-4">
           <%= image_tag('learnedpile.png', class: 'img-circle img-responsive imright') %>
            <h3>"I know it" Pile</h3>
            <h4>Things I have learned</h4>
            <p>Pile of what you have already learned. You can go to this pile and review whenever you want.</p>
            <p><%= link_to('I know it', learned_path(current_user.id), :class => "btn btn-large btn-info", :id => "indigo") %></p>
        </div>
       
    </div>
</div>    
